language ESSENCE 2.4.0

given n : int

letting S be domain int(0..n-1)

find R : function (total) (S,S) --> S

such that

$Associative
forAll i,j,k: S. R((i,R((j,k)))) = R((R((i,j)),k)),

$Commutative
forAll i,j: S. R((i,j)) = R((j,i)),

$idempotent
forAll i: S. R((i,i)) = i,

$Bounded
forAll i : S. R((0,i)) = i,
forAll i : S. R((n-1,i)) = n-1,

$Symmetry breaking
forAll i,j : S. ((R((i,j)) = i) /\ (i >= j)) \/ !(R((i,j)) = i)
